strings:
<voice_0x010012CA><se_low>King Trode: G-Good g-grief!
I d-don't think I've ever been so c-c-cold!
<voice_0x010012CB><se_low>King Trode: Sh-Shouldn't we be g-going after J-Jessica?
<voice_0x010012CC><se_low>King Trode: Then we sh-shouldn't b-be wasting our t-time here.
<voice_0x010012CD><se_low>King Trode: It's not b-because I can't stand the c-cold or anything, you understand-d-d!
<voice_0x010012CE><se_low>King Trode: C-Come on. Let's turn back. If we s-stay here any longer we'll all catch our death of c-c-c-cold.
